      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and a tune-up soon to ensure long-term reliability. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind doing a little cosmetic and mechanical work.",
